OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FYoung people in Wales are feeling
OL,7,Fincreasingly more anxious about their
OL,8,Ffuture, according to new research.
OL,10,FIt comes as youth employment rates
OL,11,Fdecreased last year.
OL,13,FAccording to The King's Trust figures,
OL,14,Fnearly three in five young people in
OL,15,FCardiff feel anxious about their
OL,16,Ffuture on a daily basis, with many
OL,17,Fciting struggling to secure stable
OL,18,Femployment as a factor.
