OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FThe new research showed young people
OL,7,Fin the Welsh capital felt uncertain
OL,8,Fabout their prospects, with 39%
OL,9,Fbelieving they will never own their
OL,10,Fown home and 32% unsure they'll earn
OL,11,Fenough to raise a family.
OL,13,FAccording to those surveyed, these
OL,14,Fconcerns have had a detrimental impact
OL,15,Fon mental health with 45% believing
OL,16,Fthat their worries have worsened their
OL,17,Fmental health.
