OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FHowever, amongst the young people who
OL,7,Fare employed, 72% said securing a job
OL,8,Fhas made them feel more optimistic
OL,9,Fabout their future.
OL,11,FThe latest Welsh Government figures,
OL,12,Fpublished in September 2024, showed
OL,13,Fthat the employment rate for young
OL,14,Fpeople aged 16 to 24 fell to 54% -
OL,15,Fdown 3.5 percentage points from the
OL,16,Fprevious year. The figures do not
OL,17,Finclude students and reflect those
OL,18,Factively looking for work.
