OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FThe statistics also highlighted gender
OL,7,Fdisparity amongst young males and
OL,8,Ffemales.
OL,10,FRio Joseph, 19, from Cardiff,
OL,11,Fexperienced months of unsuccessful job
OL,12,Fhunting which caused his mental health
OL,13,Fto suffer.
OL,15,FAfter completing a Law, Psychology and
OL,16,FSociology course at Cardiff and Vale
OL,17,FCollege, Rio was eager to start
OL,18,Fworking and saving for his future.
