OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FHowever, due to his dyslexia, he found
OL,7,Fthe application process particularly
OL,8,Fdifficult when having to write
OL,9,Fdetailed job applications.
OL,11,F"I applied for around 16 jobs over the
OL,12,Fspan of four months but didn't hear
OL,13,Fback from at least 14. Over those four
OL,14,Fmonths I began to feel like I'd never
OL,15,Ffind any sort of stable or lasting
OL,16,Fjob."
OL,18,FThe constant rejection took a toll on
OL,19,Fhis confidence.
