OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FAfter months of unsuccessful job
OL,7,Fapplications, he came across The
OL,8,FKing's Trust's TK Maxx Get Into Retail
OL,9,Fprogramme. This provided him with
OL,10,Fvital experience, which ultimately led
OL,11,Fto a role as a Loss Prevention Officer
OL,12,Fat TK Maxx.
OL,14,F"I was in such a bad place before The
OL,15,FTrust, but in trusting the process my
OL,16,Flife has transformed far better than I
OL,17,Fwould have ever expected. I'm finally
OL,18,Fproud to have found a job that I can
OL,19,Fsmile in."
