OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FThe King's Trust has stressed the need
OL,7,Ffor greater support in helping young
OL,8,Fpeople gain skills and work experience.
OL,10,FRhian Mathias, Head of Delivery at The
OL,11,FKing's Trust Wales, said: "Those not
OL,12,Fin work or education have the lowest
OL,13,Foverall wellbeing and confidence in
OL,14,Ftheir futures compared to any other
OL,15,Fgroup. Without urgent action, we risk
OL,16,Fa generation feeling locked out of
OL,17,Faccessing their potential and having
OL,18,Fstable and fulfilling lives."
