OL,3,CYoung people 'anxious' about future as
OL,4,Cyouth unemployment on the rise
OL,6,FShe added: "Despite these challenges,
OL,7,Fyoung people remain determined to
OL,8,Fsucceed. They have the ambition and
OL,9,Fpotential, and we must ensure they
OL,10,Fhave the right support, skills, and
OL,11,Fopportunities to take control of their
OL,12,Ffutures.
OL,14,F"It's crucial that we work together as
OL,15,Fa society to help young people access
OL,16,Fthe training and jobs they need, which
OL,17,Fwill not only transform their lives,
OL,18,Fbut support and benefit the local
OL,19,Fcommunities they live in and help
OL,20,Fdrive the local economy."
